---
import { Trophy } from "lucide-astro";
---

<section id="filosofia" class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden bg-brand-black">
  <!-- Background overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-premium-gradient opacity-20 z-0"></div>

  <!-- Decoration -->
  <div
    class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-brand-yellow/10 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none animate-pulse-glow"
  >
  </div>

  <div
    class="container mx-auto px-6 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center relative z-10"
  >
    <div class="relative group">
      <div
        class="relative z-10 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-brand-yellow/10 border border-white/10"
      >
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1571902943202-507ec2618e8f?q=80&w=1975&auto=format&fit=crop"
          alt="Gym Interior"
          class="w-full hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700 filter grayscale-[20%]"
        />
      </div>
      <!-- Floating Element decoration could go here -->
      <div
        class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-full h-full border border-brand-yellow/20 rounded-2xl -z-10 bg-brand-yellow/5 group-hover:translate-x-2 group-hover:translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-500"
      >
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <span
        class="text-brand-yellow font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-4 block"
        >La Filosofía +FIT</span
      >
      <h2
        class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-heading font-black mb-6 text-white leading-tight"
      >
        Más que un gimnasio, <br />
        <span class="text-brand-yellow">una familia.</span>
      </h2>
      <p
        class="text-xl text-center md:text-left text-gray-300 mb-4 leading-relaxed font-bold"
      >
        En +FIT creemos que cada persona es única.
      </p>
      <p
        class="text-xl text-gray-400 mb-8 leading-relaxed font-light text-justify md:text-left"
      >
        Por eso ofrecemos atención personalizada adaptada a tus objetivos,
        capacidades y ritmo. Nuestro equipo te acompaña en cada paso de tu
        transformación, creando un ambiente divertido donde te sientes en casa.
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        {
          [
            {
              title: "Personalizado",
              desc: "Planes diseñados específicamente para ti y tus metas.",
            },
            {
              title: "Ambiente Familiar",
              desc: "Un espacio acogedor donde todos se conocen y apoyan.",
            },
            {
              title: "Entrenar es Divertido",
              desc: "Clases dinámicas que hacen del ejercicio un momento placentero.",
            },
          ].map((item) => (
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors border border-transparent hover:border-white/5">
              <div class="mt-1 w-6 h-6 rounded-full border border-brand-yellow flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-brand-yellow rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_#FACC15]" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white tracking-wide mb-1">
                  {item.title}
                </h4>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">{item.desc}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
